context_for_next_testing_agent: Iteration 85 added major new features to Dev Control module. AI Dev Helper uses dual-model routing: GPT-4o for general queries, Claude Sonnet 4.5 for code review/architecture queries. Auto-routing keywords include 'code review', 'refactor', 'architecture', 'pattern', 'structure'. Quick actions available: health_check, security_scan, architecture_review, dependency_audit. Session data stored in 'dev_ai_sessions' and 'dev_ai_messages' MongoDB collections. DB Explorer lists all MongoDB collections. Changes Log shows git history. Dependencies shows pip list and package.json deps. Modules tab auto-detects from filesystem. All data-testid attributes properly implemented.
